{"type": "article", "id": 22636, "title": "企鹅出版纯色封面系列", "description": "", "date": "2016-02-22T10:45:24Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 33, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606150448tD0QYCFNnfp8bKd2.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">企鹅出版计划在今年 5 月出一套 20 Pocket Penguins，沿用“小黑书”（ LBC ）的版式，回归复古的纯色封面。不同的是这些书的封面采用了丰富的颜色，它们代表了不同的语言，橄榄绿代表德语，红色代表俄罗斯语，深蓝色代表法语......可以组成一个色彩丰富的调色板，非常清新。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606150445zh9UWIfa3t2YVgPN.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.54722222\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606150446kKaR8D5q9wUoWmMG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.9625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606150446xP4Qq5vTHnfWtgOh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.1475\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606150446H2oi0jbeOUhZJXQM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.10875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606150447AidRlVSctZbjCQxp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.11125\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p><br></p>\n\n\n"}